rating_comment: Nice artwork inside. Well maintained. Had a short stay.
Was an amazing stay. Wonderful hospitality. Plus the place was very clean and spacious.

Its a beautiful old world house which takes you back in the byzone era :)It has a great feel in and around with greenery and open space/pathway. It is like a 'nest' located at a corner away from the main road and walking distance from Rajdarbar hotel,Hill Cart Road.
The house is on 1st floor where we get access to a big bedroom with washroom,dining,kitchen and a sitting room.Two rooms stay locked.
There is a smart tv in the sitting room but we need to use our login/subscription for netflix etc to access it.The house has a functional kitchen,fridge and utensils incase one wants to cook too :)
Our host-Prashant Ji- is a great guy.He is very active and tries his best to make our stay comfortable.
The house is walking distance from Siliguri station so the loud siren of train/goods train is a spoiler!Also the next house has 6-8 dogs which are great to see from windows butonce they start barking then its real loud!
It definitely gives you a home away frm home feel :)!!

Prashant is a great host - helpful and responsive. There's an issue of mosquitoes around that area, however he was generous enough to provide support that mosquitoes don't create a problem. I would recommend this stay due to it being in vicinity of all major areas around.
Good place in the heart of siliguri.
The stay looks as in the photos. The host is very friendly.
Its is a nice place. I felt like home.
Great place , secluded from the hustle of the city. Would recommend to anyone looking for a place in siliguri

Prashant’s place provides all the necessities for travelers stopping in siliguri. Strong internet, restaurants close by, and a walkable distance with a backpack to siliguri station. I needed a place to pause between Darjeeling and Kolkata, this was perfect. He is immediately responsive, attentive, and clear. I highly recommend this place!

The host 'Prashant' was an amazing guy. From coordination to flexibility to additional requests, he was able to accomodate all of it. Needless to say i recommend this place to anyone who would like to feel at home, peace and surrounded by some natural beauty. Nearby junction, SNT and markets although very peaceful. Thanks to amazing hosting. The host has nailed Airbnb hosting and raised bar for best property at best price.
